Oh boy this brings back memories.  

I used to play on-hit Naut jungle.  Back when sated devourer was a thing.  Would build Devourer -> {{item:3006}} {{item:3153}} {{item:3091}} {{item:3115}} {{item:3172}} 

It was so much fun.  Sadly, burst is too strong now so if I tried that build I'd get killed in a half second before I could do anything.

He didn't really deal that whole lot of damage but it was mostly that you couldn't kill him, or that it seemed impossible to do so.

{{item:3072}} {{item:3074}} {{item:3153}} {{item:3124}}  {{item:3812}} {{item:3006}} 

The build would look something like this, note that this was before the Xin Zhao rework. Which kinda taken away that on-hit Xin Zhao playstyle. But with this build Xin Zhao would be able to solo Baron.
